name: Digital Ego TEZ#001
description:
"Augment your Digital Ego in Web 3.0 Metaverse"

The secret is to no longer see the Metaverse as something foreign, but as a new space in which people want to do many of the same things as they do now, in the same way. Then they are introduced to the experience of being part of a new reality.

— from “the Guide of Unit-153c" by the Prophet X
